\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 The shadow of a lumpy head and a dapper long-billed cap fell over the table. A voice spoke. "Who will learn to walk softly?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel looked up to find Gookin peering over the edge of the shelf.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
