\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid7472682  We}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 amish jumps from the roof. Next, honest hard-working Cugel pays off his account, though he dredges but an hour a day."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 

