\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid7472682 Malser}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278  decided to work no more, each having gleaned three scales. After dressing, they stood by the edge of the pond watching }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid12867288 Cugel}{
\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 , muttering together in low voices.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
