, mortified by his clumsy fall, in all probability had failed to notice it. This, at least, was a reasonable theory. Nevertheless, to move the scales might be judicious; he would do so at the first opportunity.}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
