\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Twango summoned Cugel to the work-room. "Cugel, tomorrow we ship four cases of prime scales at precisely noon. Go to the carpenter shop and build four stout cases to proper}{
