\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Now," said Cugel, "since from this point to the wagon I will be prime custodian of the scales, I must insist that, while all witness, }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid8748279 I}{
