\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 The procession departed the work-room and passed through a dark corridor fifteen yards long, pausing only long enough for Cugel to call ahead to Soldinck: "Is all clear?"}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "All is clear," came back Soldinck's reassurance. "You may come forward!"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
