dinck's face was grim. "Where is Twango? I wish to see him at once."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "It might be better if you returned tomorrow," said Cugel. "Twango is taking his afternoon rest."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
