\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Nearby, the eccentric towers of Flutic rose into the morning sunlight, sharp against the northern murk.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel approached the manse by a devious route, keeping to the cover of shrubs and hedges, pausing often to listen. He heard nothing; a desolate mood hung in the air.}{
