\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Almost immediately, or so it seemed, he was aroused by Codnicks the deck-boy. Blinking and yawning Cugel stumbled up to the deck, to find the sun rising and Captain Baunt impatiently pacing back and forth.
