\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel drew himself up. "I am not one to be impressed by bluster!"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "What of cudgels and pitchforks?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
