\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Tricks, full and bold!" said the mermelant. "An hour ago they sent the boy to the farm for a new wheel. They were ready to roll the old wheel into the ditch when they saw you."}{
