 to their masters as 'grooms' and 'tenders'. Ordinarily amiable, they are fond of beer, and when drunk rear high on their splayed rear legs to show their ribbed white bellies. At this juncture any slight provocation sends them into paroxysms of rage, and 
they exercise their great strength for destruction.}}}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278  They think they can trick anyone! So they send you to a sorcerer of questionable repute."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
