\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "At your urging then, I will reveal an unpleasant truth. Your reputation is that of a sly and unpredictable villain with a penchant for morbid tricks."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Faucelme gave a sad grimace. "In such a case my bare denial carries no great weight. Who are my detractors?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel smilingly shook his head. "As a gentleman of honour I must reserve this information."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Aha indeed!" said Faucelme, and became reflectively silent.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel, with half an eye always for Faucelme, took occasion to inspect the room. In addition to the side-board, the furnis
