es, and before him, from east to}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278  west, spread the estuary of the River Chaing, in a great sweep of liquid gunmetal.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
