\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 The driver spoke with unexpected spirit: "I am indeed loaded for the }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Avventura. }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
As for delay, I know of none! These are choice viands and careful selection is of the essence."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "True enough; no need to belabor the point. You have the invoice?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "I do indeed! Captain Wiskich must pay to the last terce before I unload so much as an anchovy. Those are my strict instructions."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel held up his hand. "Be easy! All will go smoothly. Captain Wiskich is conducting business over here in the}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid16670804  }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
warehouse. Come; bring your invoice."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel led the way into the old gray warehouse, now dim with dusk, and signaled the driver into the office marked }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Ticket Agent.}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 The driver peered into the office. "Captain Wiskich? Why do you sit in the dark?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel threw his cloak over the driver's head and tied him well with the wonderful extensible rope, then gagged him with his own kerchief.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel took the invoice and the fine wide-brimmed hat. "I will be back shortly; in the meantime, enjoy your rest."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel drove the dray to the }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Avventura }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
and drew up to a halt. He heard Captain Wiskich bawling to someone in the forecastle. Cugel shook his head regretfully. The risks were disproportionate to the gain; let Captain Wiskich wait.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel continued along the wharf, and across the plaza to where Varmous worked among the wagons of his caravan.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel pulled the driver's wide-brimmed hat low over his face and hid the sword under his cloak. With the invoice in hand
 he sought out Varmous. "Sir, I have delivered your load of victual, and this is the invoice, now due and payable."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Varmous, taking the invoice, read down the billing. "Three hundred and thirty terces? These are high-quality viands! My order was far more modest, and was quoted to me at two hundred terces!"}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel made a debonair gesture. "In that case, you need only pay two hundred terces," he said grandly. "We are interested only in the satisfaction of our customers."}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Varmous glanced once more at the invoice. "It is a rare bargain! But why should I argue with you?" He handed Cugel a purse. "Count it, if you like, but I assure you that it contains the proper amount."}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "That is adequate assurance," said Cugel. "I will leave the dray here and you may unload it at your convenience." He bowed and departed.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Returning to the warehouse Cugel found the driver as he had left him. Cugel said: }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid16670804 "}{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid8532196 Tzat!}{
\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 " }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 to loosen the bonds and placed the wide-brimmed hat upon the driver's head. "Do not}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid16670804  }{
\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 stir for five minutes! I will be waiting just outside the door and if you stick out your head I will lop it off with my sword. Is that clear?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Quite clear," muttered the driver.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "In that case, farewell." Cugel departed and returned to the inn where he placed down a deposit and was assigned a chamber on the balcony.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
Cugel dined upon bread and sausages, then strolled out to the front of the inn. His attention was attracted by an altercation near Varmous' caravan. Looking more closely, Cugel found Varmous in angry confrontation with Captain Wiski
ch and Yoder. Varmous refused to surrender his victuals until Captain Wiskich paid him two hundred terces plus a handling charge of fifty terces. Captain Wiskich, in a rage, aimed a blow at Varmous, who stepped aside, then struck Captain Wiskich with such
 force that he tumbled over backwards. The crew of the }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Avventura }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
was on hand and rushed forward, only to be met by Varmous' caravan personnel carrying staves, and the seamen were soundly thrashed.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Captain Wiskich, with his crew, retired into the inn to plan
 new strategies, but instead they drank great quantities of wine and committed such nuisances that they were taken by the town constables and immured in an old fortress half-way up the hill, where they were sentenced to three days of confinement.}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 When Captain Wiskich and his crew were dragged away, Cugel thought long and carefully, then went out and once more conferred with Varmous.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Earlier today, if you recall, I requested a place in your caravan."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Conditions have not changed," said Varmous shortly. "Every place is taken."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Let us suppose," said Cugel, "that you commanded another large and luxurious carriage, capable of carrying twelve in comfort \emdash  could you find enough custom to fill these places?"}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Without doubt! They now must wait for the next caravan and so will miss the Festival. But I leave in the morning and there would be no time to secure the supplies."}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "That too can be effected, if we are able to arrive at a compact."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "What do you suggest?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "I provide the carriage and the supplies. You recruit twelve more travelers and charge them premium prices. I pay nothing. We divide the net profits."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Varmous pursed his lips. "I see nothing wrong with this. Where is your carriage?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Come; we shall get it now."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Without enthusiasm Varmous followed Cugel out along the dock where finally all was quiet. Cugel boarded the }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Avventura }{
\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 and tied his rope to a ring under the bow and threw the end to Varmous. He kicked the hull with his ossip-charged boots and the vessel at once became revulsive of gravity. Debarking, Cugel
 untied the mooring lines and the vessel drifted up into the air, to the amazement of Varmous.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Stretch, line, stretch!" called Cugel and the }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Avventura }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 rose up into the darkness.}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Together Varmous and Cugel towed the ship along the road and somewhat out of town and concealed it behind the cypress trees of the graveyard; the two then returned to the inn.}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel clapped Varmous on the shoulder. "We have done a good night's work, to our mutual profit!"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "I am not apt for magic," muttered Varmous. "Weirdness makes me eery."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel waved aside his apprehensions. "Now: for a final goblet of wine to seal our compact, then a good night's sleep, and tomorrow, we set off on our journey!}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412 
