s settled his blouse, squared the hat upon his golden curls, pushed the door ajar and stepped into the cabin, with Cugel on his heels. . . . Varmous uttered a strangled cry and lurched back into Cugel, but not before Cugel discovered an acrid stench so vi
le and incisive that his teeth felt tender in their sockets.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
