 all except Nissifer, who kept to her cabin, and the mimes, who sat cross-legged beside the hull of the }{\b0\i\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Avventura }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
staring fascinated into the flames. Ivanello ap
peared in a costume of the richest quality: loose breeches of a gold, amber and black corduroy twill, fitted black boots, a loose fusk-ivory shirt embroidered with gold floriations. From his right ear, on three inches of chain, dangled a milk-opal sphere 
almost an inch in diameter: a gem which fascinated the three mimes to the edge of entrancement.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
