\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 The side-road wound back and forth up over the hills to Tuner's Gap, then turned out across a flat plain.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 The time was now almost sunset. Varmous elected to halt for the night where a stream issued from a copse of black}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid8271463  }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
