\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
"The Ildish Waste is a wild territory. We may encounter nomads down from the Karst or even the Great Erm itself. These folk, either men or half-men, are unpredictable. Therefore I am setting up a system of vigilant look-outs. Cugel, who rides the }{
