\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Clissum once again came forward, and holding high a scroll of manuscript, looked smilingly around the group.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Ivanello, leaning back into the arms of Sush, with Rlys pressed against him on one side and Skasja on the other, bent his head over his lute and drew forth a series of plangent chords.}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
