He arranged himself in a suitable posture, but the wind came in a great gust, causing the fire to wallow and flare. Clouds of smoke roiled around the area and those still present hurried away. Clissum threw his hands high
 in despair and retired from the scene.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
