eak and dry, supporting only a few stunted gong-trees, an occasional tumble of cactus, an isolated dendron, black or purple or red.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Halfway through the morning Varmous called up to the ship: "Cugel, are you keeping a sharp watch?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Cugel looked down over the gunwale. "I could watch with more purpose if I knew what I was watching for."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
