\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 I may make a demand on you for damages suffered as a result of your negligence. Here is the bill of account. You must pay over this sum at once."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
