\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "And then what occurred?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Best not to ask." Pulsifer busied himself polishing one of Phampoun's tusks with a small brush. He thrust his head forth and inspected the mottled visage above him. "Phampoun still sleeps soundly; he inge
sted a prodigous meal before retiring. Excuse me while I check the progress of Phampoun's digestion." Pulsifer ducked back behind Phampoun's wattles and revealed himself only by a vibration in the corded grey neck. Presently he returned to view. "He is qu
ite famished, or so it would appear. I had best wake him; he will wish to converse with you before. ..."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Before what?"}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "No matter."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "A moment," said Cugel. "I am interested in conversing with you rather than Phampoun."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Indeed?" asked Pulsifer, and polished Phampoun's fang}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid8544264  }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 wit}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid8544264 h}{
\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278  great vigor. "}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid8544264\charrsid8544264 Th}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid8544264 is}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278  is pleasant to hear; }{
