ted at the base of the scarp, to evoke instant outcries and curses from a human throat.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 Keeping to concealment Cugel descended the slope, to discover that the pelgrane now pursued a portly black-haired man in a suit of black and white diaper. This person a
