\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 For all his rotundity, the man showed remarkable deftness of foot and the pelgrane began to scream in frustration. It halted to glare through the crotch of the tree and snap out with its long maw.}{
\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
