The string is corroded, as if through contact with some acrid}{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid874205  }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 substance."}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
\par }{\b0\f54\fs24\cf1\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 "Most peculiar!" said Cugel.}{\b0\f54\fs24\insrsid4274412\charrsid3035278 
